name: Stand With Ukraine
description:
"Attention, Ukrainians! This is A Russian Military Ship speaking! If you don't surrender we will attack!"

"Russian Military Ship, go fuck yourself!"

This story already became a meme 

Letter Ї [yi] is a powerful symbol of Ukrainian language (and language is a keeper of tradition). Ї is present in Cyrillic UkraЇnian, but not in Russian. 

This is a gif by Vlad Koleno Golova (Knee Head) from Poltava, Ukraine. We are raising money to buy armour and ammunition for volunteer defenders of Ukraine.
